um, among others.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1172, \"end\": 1175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"score\": 0.9826111446154783, \"rank\": 0.017696555699846687, \"text\": \"MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\"}, {\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999915121407, \"rank\": 8.20004635328251e-09, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1339, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.983178384983666e-20, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Breanna Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\"}, {\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelsey_Plum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelsey Plum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelsey_Plum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelsey_Plum\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Taurasi\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\":